  "text": "Exploration strategy VIME [CITATION_1] formalizes learning progress in a bayesian way. The interest of bayesian approaches is to be able to measure the uncertainty on the learned model [CITATION_2] . Thus, the agent approximates these dynamics with a bayesian neural network [CITATION_3] , and computes the reward as the uncertainty reduction on weights. In other words, the agent tries to do actions which are informative on dynamics.",
